{{Infobox dot-com company | name = Hegarty Maths | logo = Logo_of_Educational_Website_Hegarty_Maths.jpg | company_type = [[Learning]] | foundation = | area_served = | key_people = | industry = [[Education]] | services = [[Subscription]] | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | owner = Colin Hegarty | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | url = {{url|hegartymaths.com}} | alexa = | screenshot = | caption = | website_type = Learning | language = English | advertising = | launch_date = | current_status = Live | footnotes = | intl = }} '''Hegarty Maths''' is a subscription-based [[mathematics]] website created by English mathematics teacher Colin Hegarty. <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/education/education-news/colin-hegarty-maths-teacher-could-become-a-millionaire-after-being-shortlisted-for-annual-award-a6878046.html |title=Colin Hegarty: Maths teacher could become millionaire after being shortlisted for annual award |date=17 February 2016 |author-link=https://www.independent.co.uk/author/richard-garner}}</ref> Hegarty Maths has gained creator Colin Hegarty a lot of popularity and has lead him to be shortlisted for the Varkey Foundation Global Teacher Prize. <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/ireland/colin-hegarty-worlds-best-maths-teacher-720993.html |title=Colin Hegarty – world's best maths teacher? |date=17 February 2016}}</ref> It is used by school across the UK as a replacement for general homework tasks and has positive reception from the public. <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/ireland/colin-hegarty-worlds-best-maths-teacher-720993.html |title=Colin Hegarty – world's best maths teacher? |date=20 February 2016}}</ref> ==Usage== A general task includes an educational video on a topic with some examples and a quiz to complete afterwards. The site is regularly updated to keep up with the [[GCSE]] mathematics curriculum. Teachers can assign these tasks as homework of for revision purposes. == References == {{reflist}}
